==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːt|-iːt]]

===Intransitive verb===
{{en-verb}}

#To [[violate]] rules in order to gain advantage from a situation.
#To be unfaithful to one's [[spouse]] or [[partner]].

